                                "byte_start": 28672,
                                "byte_stop": 62527,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in 74-13, Mullaney against Wilbur will be announced by Mr. Justice Powell."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 8.458,
                        "stop": 80.988,
                        "byte_start": 62527,
